849
01:23:03,603 --> 01:23:07,648
I don't... Maybe you wanna
come by and say hello?

850
01:23:07,815 --> 01:23:09,649
Around 7?

851
01:23:11,194 --> 01:23:14,363
<i>You don't have to if you don't want to.
I just, you know...</i>

852
01:23:18,451 --> 01:23:22,496
Look, I totally get if you don't wanna
hang out with the dying girl, so...

853
01:23:23,789 --> 01:23:26,958
I can... I can come at 7.

854
01:23:28,502 --> 01:23:30,302
Okay.

855
01:23:31,827 --> 01:23:33,226
Okay.

856
01:23:34,466 --> 01:23:36,051
Bye.

857
01:24:20,387 --> 01:24:23,974
- Well, how you doing tonight?
- Hey.

858
01:24:24,141 --> 01:24:26,726
- How you doing?
- Have fun.

859
01:24:27,520 --> 01:24:28,729
- Hi.
- Hi.

860
01:24:29,898 --> 01:24:31,564
Come in.

861
01:24:31,733 --> 01:24:34,025
I am so glad she's gone.

862
01:24:34,194 --> 01:24:35,903
Are you okay if we eat outside?

863
01:24:36,279 --> 01:24:37,404
Eating?

864
01:24:37,572 --> 01:24:39,030
You didn't eat already, did you?

865
01:24:39,198 --> 01:24:41,408
- No.
- Okay.

866
01:24:43,578 --> 01:24:44,619
No.

867
01:24:44,787 --> 01:24:48,039
Well, it was a surprise...

868
01:24:48,666 --> 01:24:50,542
...but you're on time.

869
01:24:52,712 --> 01:24:58,091
I haven't cooked anybody food
for years, so you better like it.

870
01:24:58,259 --> 01:25:00,219
Or lie to me.

871
01:25:03,097 --> 01:25:04,680
This is for you.

872
01:25:05,934 --> 01:25:10,395
You don't have to say anything.
I just got it... Change in there.

873
01:25:10,563 --> 01:25:14,108
